Package: shelper
Title: Helper Functions for Sanger Sequencing Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Fang", "Y", email = "fangy@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package containing helper functions and a Shiny app for Sanger sequencing analysis.
    It provides tools for chromatogram alignment, peak analysis, and primer design.
